---
title: Chicken & Creamy Red Pesto Trottle with Herby Pangrattato & Tomato Salad
description: Tonight, cosy up to this creamy, comforting bowl of curly pasta loaded with succulent chicken, garlic, crunchy pangrattato and our
moreish red pesto made of sun-dried tomato. We've even added a crisp salad to tie it all together.
